Use the standard library
This is how to Strongest_Extension of class_name and extensions:
   Remember that best is item 0 in extensions
   Remember that best_score is 0

   Remember that i is 0
   Do this extensions's length times:
      Remember that ext is item i in extensions
      Remember that score is 0

      Remember that j is 0
      Do this ext's length times:
         Remember that ch is item j in ext
         When ch is more than 64, then:
            When ch is less than 91, then:
               Increase score
            End when
         End when
         When ch is more than 96, then:
            When ch is less than 123, then:
               Decrease score
            End when
         End when
         Increase j
      End do

      When score is more than best_score, then:
         Remember that best is ext
         Remember that best_score is score
      End when
      Increase i
   End do

   Remember that answer is class_name
   Add answer to 46

   Remember that k is 0
   Do this best's length times:
      Add answer to item k in best
      Increase k
   End do

   The answer is answer
